613
00:35:32.802 --> 00:35:34.036
Charlie.

614
00:35:34.038 --> 00:35:35.871
Her name was Charlie.

615
00:35:41.344 --> 00:35:44.146
Yeah. well...

616
00:35:44.148 --> 00:35:47.482
Chucky --

617
00:35:47.484 --> 00:35:49.318
