648
00:37:27.550 --> 00:37:30.018
I'll do
anything you want. okay?

649
00:37:30.020 --> 00:37:31.887
Please.

650
00:37:37.226 --> 00:37:40.929
You don't need
to do this.

651
00:37:40.931 --> 00:37:42.964
Please.

652
00:37:47.136 --> 00:37:48.603
Yeah.

653
00:37:48.605 --> 00:37:50.872
[ Breathing heavily ]

654
